{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嗨，你好啊……马尔卡。\\n有事拜托你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "又来了！？又来修理盔甲了吗！？\\n你要弄坏到什么程度才罢休啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哎呀，抱歉啦！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可是啊，我觉得\\n你应该珍惜老主顾哦？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "赊欠修理费的家伙，\\n算不上老主顾！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "你这家伙真是的……\\n在那边等我一下。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "给你。这次可不光是修理，\\n还根据你的战斗方式，\\n进行了改良。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "噢噢，真是太棒了！\\n不愧是马尔卡！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可是，呃，怎么说呢……\\n改良的话……价格是？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "这次就……给你个特价，\\n报答你之前救了我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "可是！唯独这件事，你一定要答应我。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "盔甲不是万能的。\\n绝对不可以乱来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "因为我很害怕。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "害怕有人穿着我的盔甲受伤，\\n或是丧命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "我第一次做的盔甲……\\n是一个很年轻的士兵\\n买走的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "之后，我受军队委托，\\n前往战场修理盔甲――然后，我绝望了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "托我修的盔甲中，竟有我做的盔甲。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "被刺穿了一个大洞，\\n上面都是血……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "那是被魔法刺穿的洞。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "不管多坚固的盔甲，\\n都无法抵御魔法攻击……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "原来如此。所以，\\n你才想做最强的盔甲……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "总有一天，\\n我一定要做出最强的盔甲。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "所以，兰扎卜。\\n在我成功之前，别太乱来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "要好好珍惜自己的生命。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "知道了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "马尔卡，我期待着！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "真是的……别老敲盔甲。\\n动作真粗暴啊……嗯？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "啊啊！？都怪你这么粗暴，\\n盔甲凹进去了啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喔、嗯……抱歉。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "也就是说，这盔甲\\n还有许多地方要改良呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "可恶，我要重新研究！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "马尔卡",
            "context": "看着好了，兰扎卜！总有一天，\\n我会做出最强的盔甲给你瞧瞧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}